Methods for converting between FlowJo workspaces and cytoverse GatingSet objects

Get a table of sample groups from a flowJo workspace

Get a list of samples from a flowJo workspace

Get Keywords

Cytobank Experiments

Methods for converting between Cytobank experiments and cytoverse GatingSet objects

open_cytobank_experiment()

Construct cytobank_experiment object from ACS file

cytobank_to_gatingset(<default>) cytobank_to_gatingset(<cytobank_experiment>)

A wrapper that parses the gatingML and FCS files (or cytobank_experiment object) into GatingSet

gatingset_to_cytobank()

Convert a GatingSet to a Cytobank-compatible gatingML

ce_get_samples()

Obtain a mapping between the samples and marker panels in a Cytobank experiment

ce_get_compensations()

Obtain the spillover matrices for the samples in a Cytobank experiment

ce_get_transformations()

Obtain the transformations associated with each channel in a Cytobank experiment
